score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999984555141158, \"rank\": 1.2936835130218287e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The advertisement\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Dear Sydney\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"a dad\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"an AI-crafted letter\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"the daughter's hero\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the ad, the father asks Gemini to help create a letter \\\"telling Sydney how inspiring she is, and be sure to mention that my daughter plans on breaking her world record one day.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999984555141158, \"rank\": 1.2936835130218287e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"the father\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"her world record\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She says sorry, not sorry.)\\\"\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, the ad drew backlash from some worried about AI's role in such an emotional and personal task as writing a fan letter.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"such an emotional and personal task\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"a fan letter\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several called the message\\\"tone deaf\\\"and accused it of promoting laziness to create a letter devoid of meaning.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\\\"tone deaf\\\"and\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"laziness\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"meaning\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having a child use Gemini to write a one-time letter, that is supposed to be thoughtful, where spelling and grammar mistakes would have surely been forgiven, is just plain dumb.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \