://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reddit\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such example\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"other examples\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"the chatbot\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"her friends\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shelly Palmer, a media professor at Syracuse University,wrotein a blog post that the father in the ad was acting irresponsibly.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly Palmer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\", \"score\": 0.999999287571226, \"rank\": 3.047303280923638e-07, \"text\": \"Syracuse University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a media professor\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"a blog post\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"the father\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The father in the video is not encouraging his daughter to learn to express herself.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The father\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of guiding her to use her own words and communicate authentically, he is teaching her to rely on AI for this critical human skill,\\\" Palmer wrote.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own words\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"this critical human skill\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"Palmer\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to a request for comment, a Google spokesperson said the ad was meant to show how Gemini can provide a starting point or draft to help with the writing process.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999967948043, \"rank\": 3.205189741780178e-08, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemi